Administrativiž-territorialižikš Šrilank alajagase 9 agjaha ([[singalan kel'|singal.]] පළාත, [[tamilan kel'|tamil.]] மாகாணம்), a ned — 25 ümbrikho ([[singalan kel'|singal.]] දිස්ත්‍රි‌ක්‌ක ''Disa'', [[tamilan kel'|tamil.]] மாவட்டம் ''Māwaddam'').

== Eläjad ==
Šrilankas elädas [[lankalaižed]].

Šrilankan järedad lidnad (enamba 200 tuh. rist., 2010<ref>[http://archive.is/20130209161903/http://www.world-gazetteer.com/wg.php?x=1284053162&lng=de&des=wg&geo=-127&srt=npan&col=adhoq&msz=1500&men=gcis&lng=en Sri Lanka: largest cities and towns and statistics of their population (1981, 2001, 2007, 2010). — World-gazetteer.com.] {{ref-en}}</ref>, surembaspäi penembha): [[Kolombo]], [[Dehivala Maunt Lavinii]], [[Moratuv]]. Vl 2010 kaiked oli 24 lidnad enamba 50 tuhad eläjidenke.

== Rahvahanižanduz ==
Šrilankan päeksport om erazvuiččed [[sobad]] (läz 47%), [[čai]] (14%), [[šin]]ad da [[räzin]] (7%), toine [[maižanduz|maižandusen]] produkcii (6%: [[nižu]], [[änik]]od, [[kokospal'm|kokospähkmed]], [[kukuruz]], [[tabak]]); toine eksport — [[almaz]]ad (3%), [[laiv]]ad, [[ballast]] da [[veneh]]ed, [[kivi (material)|kived]].

